OL,5,G0900 Bargain-Loving Brits in the Sun
OL,6,     FSeries favourites Tony and
OL,7,     FMichelle swapped Essex for a new
OL,8,     Flife on the Costa Del Sol 13 years
OL,9,     Fago. They now run a business
OL,10,     Ftogether supplying awnings and
OL,11,     Fglass walls.
OL,12,G1000 Nightmare Tenants, Slum Landlords
OL,13,     FCraig has been battling to get his
OL,14,     Fproperty back after three months
OL,15,     Fof no rent. Terry was relieved to
OL,16,     Fget his home back, before Sophia
OL,17,     Fcalled the police.
