OL,5,G1100 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FIn North Yorkshire, cops look out
OL,7,     Ffor criminals and illegal drivers
OL,8,     Fmoving around under the cover of
OL,9,     Fdarkness. After a spike in
OL,10,     Fcatalytic converter thefts, a
OL,11,     Fstinger is used.
OL,12,G1200 Traffic Cops
OL,13,     FThe cops deal with a major drugs
OL,14,     Fbust, a man linked to an alleged
OL,15,     Fassault on a woman, and a gang of
OL,16,     Fsuspected poachers with an
OL,17,     Fun-taxed van.
