OL,5,G1300 Traffic Cops
OL,6,     FOver a Bank Holiday, near
OL,7,     FScarborough, a high-speed pursuit
OL,8,     Fensues after a driver fails to
OL,9,     Fstop. In the Dales, an operation
OL,10,     Fis underway to crack down on
OL,11,     Fmotorists flouting the law.
OL,12,G1400 Police Interceptors
OL,13,     FThe interceptors come knocking for
OL,14,     Fa suspected drugs dealer who's
OL,15,     Fbeen on the run for two years.
OL,16,G1500 Police Interceptors
OL,17,     FWhen a dog handler is taken out of
OL,18,     Fthe chase, multiple cops and the
OL,19,     Fpolice chopper take up the hunt
OL,20,     Ffor a driver who flees on foot.
