OL,5,G1830 Home and Away
OL,6,     FDavid confides in Amelia. Beau
OL,7,     Fwants Harper all to himself.
OL,8,     FRichie makes a tough decision.
OL,9,G1900 GPs: Behind Closed Doors
OL,10,     FIn Peterborough, a pair of cyclist
OL,11,     Fbrothers receive medical support
OL,12,     Fafter being knocked off their
OL,13,     Fbikes by a van, and Dr Devin Gray
OL,14,     Fis concerned about a patient's
OL,15,     Fdramatic weight loss.
OL,16,G2000 Casualty 24/7: Every Second Counts
OL,17,     FJunior Doctor Tom's first patient
OL,18,     Fis 18-year-old Lewis who has
OL,19,     Fbroken bones and deep wounds from
OL,20,     Fa moped accident - but causing him
OL,21,     Fthe most pain is his fear of
OL,22,     Fneedles.
